Description: The parameter SkuCapacity was changed from long to nullable long to prevent a scenario which no value is passed and 0 value is being used
Remediation: The cmdlet 'Update-AzOperationalInsightsCluster' no longer supports the type 'System.Int64' for parameter 'SkuCapacity'.","Change the type for parameter 'SkuCapacity' back to 'System.Int64'.
